uT5Sicx3eN2_adW9ZDa5py9N7tnKNi_S6xkDnHFgWsgcs1Yo6m3SIXtodJ4&amp;fref=nf&amp;__xts__[0]=68.ARCDQS388iO1LKMYvpXrecNYS5xaKvbsL97qsUPlOqEMrbuMtLvM8PW7EQVQO1jbLlkHuJAigF12XxzDaZaMgXrtwgYwC4bgyLJ_GoO00qGbo5zeMrNk9fL9b-4KKAYt_mq-eImGkPudwq1kT1zP-As5iJ-LkDwjAT5pPk8-KlaSN7mcTl7MYYG6xQfV3vVaIQSfwQ5CxCrKOhzwBnhpTLt8wklELtJ4zEtAU2M1QGA_SndwQYIMKYoMuWCWzZHFJU-yIbRSjMC0slzefuZ4XikjzmV5dtxNcgj0KaAc1WXsJZRfyieMmTk2TXuSgrJZ1G68f6KWA-u_IC5N2tVOI6dQQ39qlnwrAq-J2fxQVK908UfpKgQQhMKL</a><br />\n<br />\n【緊急呼籲：兩歳中徳混血兒急求骨髓捐贈】<br />\n*** Urgent Appeal for Bone Marrow Donor for 2-year-old German-Chinese Girl***<br />\n<br />\n德裔爸爸和港人媽媽的兩歳獨生女Livia 因患罕見血癌，急需六月前找到合適的骨髓延續生命。Livia 家人祈求各位有心人幫忙，讓Livia繼續有機會感受、經歷世間上一切美好事物，探求未知的未來。<br />\n2-year-old Livia, born to a German father and a Chinese mother, was diagnosed with acute leukemia and will only survive if she undergoes a bone marrow transplant before June. Doctors are trying to match Livia to a donor, but this is made harder due to her mixed-race background. Her family desperately need your help and are immensely grateful for your attention for the below.<br />\n<br />\n1. 如您本人是或認識中德混血人士或家庭，請直接聯絡 Ms Yu (+852-5415 2298/ 999livia999@gmail.com.) 。取得同意後，簡單的血液測試便能辨認出合適捐贈者。<br />\nIf you are, or know any Chinese-German mixed race persons or families, please get in touch directly with Ms Yu at +852-5415 2298/ 999livia999@gmail.com. With your consent, a simple blood test can be done to determine potential donors.<br />\n<br />\n2. 其他人士亦可到附近的 香港紅十字會 Hong Kong Red Cross 進行簡單驗血及登記成為骨髓捐贈者。香港紅十字會的骨髓捐贈者資料庫與世界連接，有心人只要到捐血中心填妥骨髓捐贈者資料庫同意書，就能幫助Livia盡快找到合適的骨髓。<br />\nFor everyone else, YOU can still be a match. Please head to the nearest Red Cross, do a simple blood test and register to be a bone marrow donor. The registry runs globally, so a match CAN happen in Hong Kong. This simple 30-minute procedure can potentially save Livia's life.<br />\n<br />\n關於 Livia 的捐贈呼籲已得到本地各大媒體報導。想了解更多詳情，請參考 Saving little Livia 救救小女孩Livia 專頁。<br />\nLivia's appeal has been reported in various local media. For more about her story and details on donor registration, please go to Saving little Livia 救救小女孩Livia<br />\n<br />\n傳媒報導/ Media coverage:<br />\nThe Standard 英文虎報: <a href=\"http://www.thestandard.com.hk/&hellip;/Clock-ticks-for-two-year-old-in-bo&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandard.com.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2FClock-ticks-for-two-year-old-in-bo%E2%80%A6&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=ef405f5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.thestandard.com.hk/&hellip;/Clock-ticks-for-two-year-old-in-bo&hellip;</a><br />\nTOPick 新聞: <a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/2612168/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2612168%2F&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=f7de2f10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">topick.hket.com/article/2612168/</a><br />\n01親子: <a href=\"https://t1p.de/qnyq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft1p.de%2Fqnyq&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=f6f7ae05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t1p.de/qnyq</a>"},{"pid":"f9c8b8a674fc8c895805f80cd6227de8eaa324e0","tid":1963912,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877fe67fdc32a8a6ffc6a37cfa7184ba0acc4bdb","tid":1963912,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e387c1d0f483dd9828b6e49286b987c17e4f99d4","tid":1963912,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a79d3d650bc46bcbbfa38cd216c413bfa68a3e0","tid":1963912,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e4c